messages.message: Some of the most interesting docs that I want to try are often more than 10MB. I've been using an online tool to compress PDFs and then upload - PDF compressor: Compress PDFs online for free | Adobe Acrobat (https://www.adobe.com/acrobat/online/compress-pdf.html). I wonder if we should try to bump up this limit or have an error message recommending a compression tool? @Xi Cheng

@avi should there be limits on the number of pages in the document, with probably a higher limit on the document size. Our processing times and resourcing are more constrained by the number of pages then the size of documents.
